text: Arnaud may refer to: ==People== * Arnaud (given name) or Arnauld (formerly Arnoul), the French form of the German given name Arnold * Arnaud (surname) or Arnauld (formerly Arnoul), the French form of the name Arnold * Arnauld family, a noble French family prominent in the 17th century, associated with Jansenism ==Places== * Arnaud, Nippes, a commune in Haiti * Arnaud River (formerly known as the Payne River), a river in Nunavik, Quebec, Canada == Other uses == * Arnaud's, a well known restaurant in New Orleans, Louisiana, U.S. * Saint Arnaud (disambiguation) ==See also== * Arnie (disambiguation) * Arnold (disambiguation)
title: Arnaud
